@(73-79=c4073.73) The mistress, a leopard among the @wDN{Anuna} gods, full of pride, has been given authority. Not having …… struggle ……, @wDN{Inana} ……. She …… the adolescent girl in her chamber, receiving her, …… heart …… charms. She evilly …… the woman she rejects. In the entire (?) country she ……. She lets her run around in the town square ……. …… of a house the wife sees her child.

@(80-90=c4073.80) When she had removed the great punishment from her body, she invoked blessings upon it; she caused it to be named the @fsux{pilipili}. She broke the spear and as if she were a man …… gave her a weapon. When she had …… punishment, it is not ……. She …… the door of the house of wisdom, she makes known its interior. Those who do not respect her suspended net do not escape …… when she suspends the meshes of her net. The man she has called by name she does not hold in esteem. Having approached the woman, she breaks the weapon and gives her a spear. The male @fsux{ŋišgisaŋkeš}, the @fsux{nisub} and the female @fsux{ŋišgi} ritual officiants, after having …… punishment, moaning ……. The ecstatic, the transformed @fsux{pilipili}, the @fsux{kurŋara} and the @fsux{saŋursaŋ} ……. Lament and song ……. They exhaust themselves with weeping and grief, they …… laments.

@(91-98=c4073.91) Weeping daily your heart does not ……. 'Alas' …… heart …… knows no relaxation. Beloved lady of holy @wDN{An}, your …… in weeping ……. In heaven ……. On your breast ……. You alone are majestic, you have renown, heaven and earth …… not ……. You rival @wDN{An} and @wDN{Enlil}, you occupy their seat of honour. You are pre-eminent in the cult places, you are magnificent in your course.

@(99-108=c4073.99) @wDN{Ezina} …… august dais ……. @wDN{Iškur} who roars from the sky ……. His thick clouds ……. When …… the great divine powers of heaven and earth, @wDN{Inana}, your victory is terrifying ……. The @wDN{Anuna} gods bow down in prostration, they abase themselves. You ride on seven great beasts as you come forth from heaven. Great @wDN{An} feared your precinct and was frightened of your dwelling-place. He let you take a seat in the dwelling-place of great @wDN{An} and then feared you no more, saying: @q[An,Inana]{“I will hand over to you the august royal rites and the great divine rites.”}

@(109-114=c4073.109) The great gods kissed the earth and prostrated themselves. The high mountain land, the land of cornelian and lapis lazuli, bowed down before you, but @wGN{Ebiḫ} did not bow down before you and did not greet you. Shattering it in your anger, as desired, you smashed it like a storm. Lady, pre-eminent through the power of @wDN{An} and @wDN{Enlil}, ……. Without you no destiny at all is determined, no clever counsel is granted favour.

@(115-131=c4073.115) To run, to escape, to quiet and to pacify are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To rove around, to rush, to rise up, to fall down and to …… a companion are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To open up roads and paths, a place of peace for the journey, a companion for the weak, are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To keep paths and ways in good order, to shatter earth and to make it firm are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To destroy, to build up, to tear out and to settle are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To turn a man into a woman and a woman into a man are yours, @wDN{Inana}. Desirability and arousal, bringing goods into existence and establishing properties and equipment are yours, @wDN{Inana}. Profit, gain, great wealth and greater wealth are yours, @wDN{Inana}. Profit and having success in wealth, financial loss and reduced wealth are yours, @wDN{Inana}. 
