@(132-154=c4073.132) …… mercy and pity are yours, @wDN{Inana}. …… are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To cause the …… heart to tremble, …… illnesses are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To have a favourite wife, ……, to love …… are yours, @wDN{Inana}. Rejoicing, being haughty, …… are yours, @wDN{Inana}. Neglect and care, raising and bowing down are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To build a house, to create a woman's chamber, to possess implements, to kiss a child's lips are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To run, to race, to plot and to succeed are yours, @wDN{Inana}. To interchange the brute and the strong and the weak and the powerless is yours, @wDN{Inana}. To interchange the heights and valleys, and raising up and reducing, is yours, @wDN{Inana}. To give the crown, the throne and the royal sceptre is yours, @wDN{Inana}.
