@(243-253=c4073.243) Advice ……, grief, bitterness ……, 'alas' ……. My lady, …… mercy …… compassion …… I am yours! This will always be so! May your heart be soothed towards me! May your understanding …… compassion. May …… in front of you, may it be my offering. Your divinity is resplendent in the Land! My body has experienced your great punishment. Bitter lament keeps me awake with …… anxiety. Mercy, compassion, care, lenience and homage are yours, and to cause flood storms, to open hard ground and to turn darkness into light.

@(254-263=c4073.254) My lady, let me proclaim your magnificence in all lands, and your glory! Let me praise your ways and greatness! Who rivals you in divinity? Who can compare with your divine rites? May great @wDN{An}, whom you love, say for you @q[An,Inana]{“It is enough!”}. May the great gods calm your mood. May the lapis lazuli dais, fit for ladyship, ……. May your magnificent dwelling place say to you: @q[dwelling place,Inana]{“Be seated”}. May your pure bed say to you: @q[bed,Inana]{“Relax”}. Your ……, where @wDN{Utu} rises, …….

@(264-271=c4073.264) They proclaim your magnificence; you are the lady ……. @wDN{An} and @wDN{Enlil} have determined a great destiny for you throughout the entire universe. They have bestowed upon you ladyship in the assembly chamber. Being fitted for ladyship, you determine the destiny of noble ladies. Mistress, you are magnificent, you are great! @wDN{Inana}, you are magnificent, you are great! My lady, your magnificence is resplendent. May your heart be restored for my sake!

